Hi Ted,

There's a fitting on the driver's side rail already there for a guage. 
Just unscrew the bolt plugging it, save it in a safe place, then install 
the guage.

I've had one on my bus since my FI install in 2005. It's a very helpful 
diagnostic tool.

Happy Trails,

